    <div xlink:href="41467_2018_4738_Article_Equ3.gif" position="anchor" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
   </div>
  </div>with 
  <span class="italic">p</span>(
  <span class="italic">s</span>′|
  <span class="italic">s</span>, 
  <span class="italic">π</span>(
  <span class="italic">s</span>)) being the probability to enter state 
  <span class="italic">s</span>′ given the agent has started in state s and applied action 
  <span class="italic">π</span>(
  <span class="italic">s</span>).
 </p>
